# ── Deployment secrets — NEVER commit (Phase 2) ──
shulehq_admin_key
shulehq_admin_key.pub
shulehq_ci_key
shulehq_ci_key.pub
*.pem
deploy/.env.production
# The TEMPLATE is placeholders only and must be committed -- it is the sole
# record of why these values are what they are (JWT carry-over, the Daraja
# mock hazard, Turnstile rollout). The `.env.*` rule above was silently
# swallowing it, so the documentation existed on one laptop and nowhere else.
!deploy/.env.production.example
deploy/*.env
